 22	/* This module provides a separate process to run system().
 23	 * The communication between this process and the main processing
 24	 * is done through unix pipes.
 25	 *
 26	 * Motivation: the UE sets its IP address using system() and
 27	 * that disrupts realtime processing in some cases. Having a
 28	 * separate process solves this problem.
 29	 */
